      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract><t:p>The Story of Melchizedek is an apocryphal account of the life of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6988Melchize">Melchizedek</t:persName>, an originally Greek text (spuriously attributed to <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2209Athanasi">Athanasius</t:persName> in a
            minority of Greek and Arabic manuscripts) attested in a Geʿez version (probably
            from Arabic), also attested in Coptic, Syriac, Arabic, Armenian and Georgian.
         </t:p>
         </t:abstract>
